#| msgid ""
#| "Kolf is a miniature golf game. The game is played from an overhead view, "
#| "with a hort bar representing the golf club. Kolf features many different "
#| "types of objects, such water hazards, slopes, sand traps, and black holes "
#| "(warps), among others."
msgid ""
"Kolf is a miniature golf game. The game is played from an overhead view, "
"with a short bar representing the golf club. Kolf features many different "
"types of objects, such water hazards, slopes, sand traps, and black holes "
"(warps), among others."
msgstr ""
"Kolf je igra minijaturnog golfa. Igra se preko pogleda odozgo, i sa prečkom "
"koja predstavlja palicu za golf. Kolf sadrži mnoge vrste objekata, poput "
"vodenih prepreka, kosina, peščanih zamki i crnih rupa (crvotočina)."

